Interface VirtualMachineScaleSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GroupableResource, Indexable, Refreshable<VirtualMachineScaleSet>, Resource, Updatable<VirtualMachineScaleSet.UpdateStages.WithPrimaryLoadBalancer>, Wrapper<com.microsoft.azure.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineScaleSetInner>

    public interface VirtualMachineScaleSet
extends GroupableResource, Refreshable<VirtualMachineScaleSet>, Wrapper<com.microsoft.azure.management.compute.implementation.VirtualMachineScaleSetInner>, Updatable<VirtualMachineScaleSet.UpdateStages.WithPrimaryLoadBalancer>
